{
  "stem": "14463.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My uncle, my auntie, my two cousins, my mother and I in one room, and it was even more primitive then Chrzanow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The woman had-- she used-- the lady of the house used to have a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, a-- that was a casket, a wooden casket, like a 40-- 40-gallon casket.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Like you've got-- wine, you know, like this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She had water in it from the river somewhere she took the water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And carps were swimming inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was for-- for Shabbos, you know, for Shabbos to cook for Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And from that, we were eating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were drinking that water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And was cooking from that water and we washed ourselves with that water.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everything from that little-- from that little thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we stay-- and the war-- and that's where we stayed when the war finished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How long we stayed there is approximately-- I would say two months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Approximately two months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right, now that's a big story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's a big story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the Germans were very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Straightaway, they have got [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, in Polish was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You mustn't do this, you should do this, you can't do that, if you don't do something like this, then you'll be shot, right?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So straight away, you can't go to a shop to buy whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So straight away, we're hungry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was number one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then came another decree that was the most important decree.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was after one week we were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Big placards everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People which do not-- which were not born [? in Shemishel ?] and didn't live in-- before the war in the city have got to go back to the cities where they actually came from.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
